;

    298k-sy.res created by SHELXL-2014/7

TITL sy_dabco_en_hclo4_1_rt_cu_a.res in Cmc2(1)
REM Old TITL SY_dabco_EN_HClO4_1_RT_Cu in Cmc2(1)
REM SHELXT solution in Cmc2(1)
REM R1 0.165, Rweak 0.040, Alpha 0.004, Orientation as input
REM Flack x = -0.209 ( 0.145 ) from Parsons' quotients
REM Formula found by SHELXT: C9 N2 O13 Cl4
CELL 1.54184 8.0949 24.7197 10.1955 90 90 90
ZERR 4 0.0001 0.0003 0.0001 0 0 0
LATT -7
SYMM -X,-Y,0.5+Z
SYMM +X,-Y,0.5+Z
SYMM -X,+Y,+Z
SFAC C H Cl N O
UNIT 32 96 16 16 64
EQIV $1 0.5-X,1.5-Y,0.5+Z
EQIV $2 1.5-X,1.5-Y,0.5+Z
EQIV $3 -1+X,+Y,1+Z
EQIV $4 -1+X,+Y,+Z
EQIV $5 1-X,1-Y,0.5+Z
EQIV $6 0.5-X,1.5-Y,-0.5+Z

L.S. 20
PLAN  20
